Amanda Berry, 29, and Gina DeJesus, 25, have written a book, Hope: A Memoir of Survival in Cleveland, which will be released on April 27 .
The brave women have written about the years of rapes, torture and psychological games at the hands of Ariel Castro, a man who lived close to their homes in Cleveland .
They have written that Castro was much stronger than he looked, packing muscle beneath his rotund figure .